The paper deals with the classification of histopathological images using various image descriptors and machine learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep features and bag-of-visual words (BoVW) also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential of using these techniques for medical imaging, which could also relate to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
